name: Die Fast (helloguysmaster)
description:
Die Fast! is a game where you have to die fast! Made for the Weekly Game Jam 130.

The game is also open source, though in order to use the project you must already have gamemaker. While the code isn't the best, I'd say it's pretty decent for a game jam.

Sources (for art and music):

Coin: https://opengameart.org/content/spinning-coin-1616-16x16

Bullet: https://opengameart.org/content/bullets-game-asset

Spike: https://opengameart.org/content/bevouliin-free-game-obstacle-spikes

Coin Sound: https://freesound.org/people/cabled_mess/sounds/350876/

Doomer Russian Music: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=11DXUv-AW3w&list=PLdx8EXsWdhKCbLvU5ICNsTcqaGQfi4APs&index=2&t=0s
